      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "これも……イメージと違うな。うーん\n莉央はいつもどんなパンケーキを食べてたっけ……？",
      "startTime": 5.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2519.9999999999995,
          "startTime": 3.32
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6066.6666667,
          "startTime": 6.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "このパンケーキ、クリームの甘さが絶妙ね！",
      "startTime": 11.8743082364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "生地もしっとりしていて……\nフルーツとの相性も悪くないわ",
      "startTime": 18.7589796384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。パンケーキを食べてる莉央は\n本当に幸せそうだ",
      "startTime": 25,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "……何？　葵も私を見てないで食べたらどうなの？\nこれ、凄く美味しいわよ",
      "startTime": 31.8611347835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living-01-000-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "――うん、ダメだ。メニューは思い出せないや\nとりあえず、それっぽいのを作ってみるか",
      "startTime": 42.2666675568,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3872.4719046999994,
          "startTime": 46.1391394615
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ただいまー、あれ？\n今日は葵が夕飯当番だったの？",
      "startTime": 51.2058051109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ。作りたいものがあって\nあ……そうだ。ちょうど良かった",
      "startTime": 57.7866653603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "うん。怜になら任せられると思う\nダンスがうまい人は料理がうまいって決まってるんだ",
      "startTime": 65.4666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "どういう理論なのよ……\nダンスのうまさと料理は関係なくない？",
      "startTime": 72.3844035785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "一緒なら、限りなく理想に近づける気がする\n僕に力を貸してほしい",
      "startTime": 80.7666701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "忙しいのも分かってる\nでもこれは、怜と僕にしか出来ない。だから、お願い",
      "startTime": 85.3000034333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "まだよく分からないけど……\nそこまで言うなら手伝ってあげなくもないわ",
      "startTime": 94.3384406089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、助かるよ\n怜が来たから百人力だね",
      "startTime": 101.100002416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……なるほど。莉央さんのパンケーキ\n葵が作ることにしたのね",
      "startTime": 110.5232479094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央が食べたことないものって\n簡単なようで意外と難しいんだ",
      "startTime": 115.4000049592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、食べたことあるものから考えるのはどう？\nいつも注文するパンケーキをベースにしてみるとか",
      "startTime": 124.1012563704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "カラフルなクリームが乗っていたり\nベリーや柑橘系のフルーツが沢山使われてたり……",
      "startTime": 131.1012563704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんがいつも頼むメニュー、覚えてないの？",
      "startTime": 135.251183335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "……全然思い出せない\n莉央が楽しそうだったことは覚えてるんだけど",
      "startTime": 143.8666731518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "……まあ、いいわ\nそれじゃあ、素材にこだわってみるのは？",
      "startTime": 150.4619713464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "それも考えた。でも、今から岡山まで行って\nマスカットを買ってくるのは無理じゃないか",
      "startTime": 159.5333520254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "誰もそこまでやれとは……はあ\n出来る範囲でいいと思うわよ",
      "startTime": 169.1566425958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "アイシングクッキーとか飾りにこだわってみたりね\nチョコレートアートもいいんじゃない？",
      "startTime": 176.6566425958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "飾りね……もうこれでいいんじゃないかな",
      "startTime": 179.2133265335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "生地が虹色のパンケーキ！？\nカラフルなクリームも相まって毒々しく見えるわね",
      "startTime": 187.8244431494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "驚きはするけど、喜ぶかどうかは別じゃない？\n……葵、めんどくさくなってきてるでしょ",
      "startTime": 201.1577764827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "……とにかく、作らないことにはアイデアも出ない\nリズムに乗らないと踊れない。ダンスみたいにさ",
      "startTime": 210.7999993643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスと一緒にするのはどうかと思うけど……\nそうね。手を動かしてから考えましょ",
      "startTime": 218.5024281183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、生地作りをしようか\n卵と牛乳、パンケーキミックスを混ぜて",
      "startTime": 225.1333326977,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-03.m4a",
          "delay": 12235.152975500001,
          "startTime": 234.5436296779
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-03.m4a",
          "delay": 5458.189964300004,
          "startTime": 227.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-03.m4a",
          "delay": 4318.341191399981,
          "startTime": 229.4516738891
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-03.m4a",
          "delay": 9410.296980199973,
          "startTime": 234.5436296779
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "……あら、おかしいわね\n全然、ダマが消えない……",
      "startTime": 234.5436296779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
